+On all
+        Enable network SysRq by writing a cookie to icmp_echo_sysrq, e.g.::
+
+                echo 0x01020304 >/proc/sys/net/ipv4/icmp_echo_sysrq
+
+        Send an ICMP echo request with this pattern plus the particular
